http://www.dft.gov.uk/consultations/dft-20090917,Traffic Signs (Amendment) Regulations and General Directions 2010 and the Traffic Signs (Temporary Obstruction) Regulations 2010,Consultation document on the Traffic Signs (Amendment) Regulations and General Directions 2010 and the Traffic Signs (Temporary Obstruction) Regulations 20,"## Summary

Consultation document on the Traffic Signs (Amendment) Regulations and General Directions 2010 and the Traffic Signs (Temporary Obstruction) Regulations 2010.

## Further information

Please note that the Consultation Document and the draft Impact Assessment have been updated from those originally issued on 17 September. 

The closing date for this consultation has also been extended to 24 December 2009. The Consultation Document has been revised to clarify the proposals for savings for signs that are being withdrawn - see page 17. 

The Impact Assessment has been revised to include the Traffic Signs (Temporary Obstructions) (Amendment) Regulations 2010 in the title. 

It has also been revised to reflect the fact that the draft Statutory Instruments apply to Scotland as well as England and Wales. No changes have been made to the draft Statutory Instruments or to the consultation proposals. 

 

