http://www.dft.gov.uk/consultations/dft-20091210a,Regulating Air Transport: Consultation on Proposals to Update the Regulatory Framework for Aviation,This consultation sets out the Government’s proposals for modernising the civil aviation regulatory framework.,"## Summary

This consultation sets out the Government's proposals for modernising the civil aviation regulatory framework. This consultation builds on the proposals for reforming the economic regulation of airports in the UK which we [consulted](http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/tna/20100927131008/http://www.dft.gov.uk/consultations/archive/2009/ukairports/)on earlier this year.

The consultation period has been extended from 11 March 2010 to 18 March 2010.

Please note that the consultation document is available to download in full and by chapter.

